{"title":"世纪伟人  ——恩来同志百年诞辰纪念","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":3,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"世纪伟人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——恩来同志百年诞辰纪念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个人的降生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱动着大时代的车轮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个人的逝世，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭痛了亿万人的赤心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的诞辰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们追思绵绵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的忌日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们泪雨纷纷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脉搏的跳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叩响祖国奋进的节奏；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼吸的频律，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关联整个民族的命运。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为您和人民大众"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是血肉相连；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为您和领导集体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是密不可分。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今呵而今，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍奔忙着您英武的身影；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界各处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还长留着您闪光的脚印。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和蔼的笑容，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已化为不谢的花朵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲切的话语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已化为回荡的乐音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那巍巍山峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不就是您坚劲的骨骼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那滚滚江河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不就是您热血在沸腾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那浩浩海洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不就是您冥思的大脑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那茫茫宇宙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不就是您广阔的胸襟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百年很短很短，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵目一览世纪风云；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百年很长很长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄立您这世纪伟人！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}